{"type":null,"faqId":31836,"title":"如何群发短信？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:1.6736112in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.6736112in;margin-top:0.22222222in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.6736112in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p7{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.009722223in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>按照下列步骤操作：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕界面，点击“信息 &gt; </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98915\" style=\"width:0.33333334in;height:0.24166666in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> ”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>在收件人输入框中添加多个收件人：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">−  </span><span>点击收件人输入框可输入多个收信人号码。每输入一个号码后点击“；”以隔开各联系人。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">−  </span><span>点击收件人输入框右边的 “</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98916\" style=\"width:0.2576389in;height:0.18541667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> ” 可添加多个收信人。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">图1-1</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98917\" style=\"width:3.023611in;height:4.423611in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>点击“输入信息”输入短信内容。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>点击“ </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98918\" style=\"width:0.34236112in;height:0.24444444in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>” 群发短信。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98919\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6356","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1435287937000,"seriesProductName":"DAV-703L","visitedTimes":45,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"群发短信","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}